title: 101 Strings - The Best of Ballroom: Shall We Dance 2CD
description:
There are not many Ballroom dancing CD's ripped and those that are ripped are typically cheesy sounding like someone played a keyboard to make the entire CD. Well, get ready to dance to an actual orchestra. This compilation is by 101 Strings, or more acurately the New 101 Strings unless the orchestra is made up of zombies.

There's a DVD as part of this set. Let Big Papi know if you'd like to have that uploaded.

And actually, the band playing this may be The Ballroom Band. 101 Strings is definitely on the DVD but Big Papi can't confirm it is also on the CD's.

P.S. Most of the songs are Latin. Search Big Papi Latin for more music.

- Big Papi
